subject: College Athletics
Basketball
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Adrian Ritchie scored 18 points to lead five teammates in double figures and No. 13 Wisconsin-Green Bay earned a trip to the N.C.A.A. tournament with a victory over Butler.
